Changes:
 ros-one-moveit-opw-kinematics-plugin (0.4.0-4-gfa51c00-2024.10.10.17.35) jammy; urgency=high
 .
   * Update status badge noetic-devel (default) branch
   * Run melodic ci job on ubuntu 18.04
